ure auth toggle enabled\n gateway.controlUi.allowInsecureAuth=true does not bypass secure context or device identity checks; only dangerouslyDisableDeviceAuth disables Control UI device…\n Fix: Disable it or switch to HTTPS (Tailscale Serve) or localhost.\n WARN Insecure or dangerous config flags enabled\n Detected 3 enabled flag(s): gateway.controlUi.allowInsecureAuth=true, gateway.controlUi.dangerouslyAllowHostHeaderOriginFallback=true, gateway.controlUi.danger…\n Fix: Disable these flags when not actively debugging, or keep deployment scoped to trusted/local-only networks.\n… +2 more\nFull report: openclaw security audit\nDeep probe: openclaw security audit --deep\n\nChannels\n┌──────────┬─────────┬────────┬─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ Channel │ Enabled │ State │ Detail │\n├──────────┼─────────┼────────┼─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│ Telegram │ ON │ OK │ token config (8313…woqE · len 46) · accounts 1/1 │\n└──────────┴─────────┴────────┴─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n\nSessions\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┬────────┬─────────┬──────────────┬───────────────────┐\n│ Key │ Kind │ Age │ Model │ Tokens │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┼────────┼─────────┼──────────────┼───────────────────┤\n│ agent:main:main │ direct │ 1m ago │ coder-model │ 9.7k/128k (8%) │\n│ agent:main:telegram:group:@webc… │ group │ 13h ago │ coder-model │ unknown/128k (?%) │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┴────────┴─────────┴──────────────┴───────────────────┘\n\nFAQ: https://docs.openclaw.ai/faq\nTroubleshooting: https://docs.openclaw.ai/troubleshooting\n\nNext steps:\n Need to share? openclaw status --all\n Need to debug live? openclaw logs --follow\n Need to test channels? openclaw status --deep"}],"timestamp":1772857553612},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户运行了 `openclaw status`，我可以看到：\n\n1. 只有一个 Telegram 渠道启用\n2. 没有 webchat 渠道配置\n3. 有两个会话：main 会话和一个 telegram group 会话\n\n问题是用户想让我用百度搜索，但我没有直接调用百度搜索的权限。根据系统提示，我有 `baidu-search` 技能的描述，但没有实际执行搜索的工具。\n\n让我检查可用的工具：\n- message: 发送消息\n- sessions_list: 列出会话\n- sessions_history: 获取会话历史\n- sessions_send: 发送消息到另一个会话\n- session_status: 显示会话状态\n\n确实没有直接的搜索工具。我需要告诉用户这个情况，或者建议他们如何配置。\n\n另外，我注意到用户是在 Control UI 中与我交互，但消息工具尝试发送到 \"webchat\" 或 \"openclaw-control-ui\" 都失败了。这是因为当前只有 Telegram 渠道配置了。\n\n让我给用户一个清晰的解释和解决方案。"},{"type":"text","text":"看到了！问题清楚了：\n\n**当前配置情况：**\n- ✅ Telegram 渠道已启用\n- ❌ WebChat 渠道未配置（所以消息发送失败）\n- ❌ 百度搜索技能未安装/未启用\n\n**解决方案：**\n\n1. **启用 WebChat 渠道**（这样我们就能直接对话）：\n   ```bash\n   openclaw channels enable webchat\n   ```\n\n2. **安装百度搜索技能**：\n   ```bash\n   clawhub install baidu-search\n   ```\n\n3. **或者临时方案**：如果你想继续用 Telegram 对话，我可以通过 Telegram 渠道回复你。\n\n你想先做哪个？我建议先启用 WebChat，这样我们在 Control UI 里就能正常交流了！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen-portal","model":"coder-model","stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772857553613},{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"你之前的聊天记录对应的配置如何恢复"}],"timestamp":1772878601158},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问的是如何恢复之前的聊天记录配置。从 session_status 的输出可以看到有两个会话：\n1. agent:main:main - 直接会话，1分钟前活跃\n2. agent:main:telegram:group:@webc… - 群组会话，13小时前活跃\n\n用户可能指的是之前在 Telegram 群组的聊天记录配置。让我先查看会话列表和历史记录来了解情况。\n\n我需要：\n1. 查看会话列表，了解有哪些会话\n2. 检查是否有之前的会话历史可以恢复\n3. 帮助用户理解配置情况\n\n让我先调用 sessions_list 来查看当前会话状态。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_226bb334cc8d46d1b7153d04","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"limit":10,"messageLimit":5}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen-portal","model":"coder-model","stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772878601160}]}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772878604508}}
{"type":"message","id":"e9e22747","parentId":"5197d353","timestamp":"2026-03-07T10:16:49.641Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"从会话列表可以看到：\n1. 当前只有一个活跃会话 (agent:main:main)\n2. 之前在 `openclaw status` 输出中提到的 Telegram 群组会话 (agent:main:telegram:group:@webc…) 没有出现在列表中，可能是因为它不是当前 agent:main 的直接会话\n\n用户问的是如何恢复之前的聊天记录配置。从之前的 status 输出看，有一个 Telegram 群组会话是 13 小时前活跃的。\n\n让我获取那个 Telegram 会话的历史记录，看看能否帮助用户恢复配置。不过我需要正确的 sessionKey。\n\n从之前的 status 输出，session key 看起来是 `agent:main:telegram:group:@webc…`（被截断了）。让我尝试获取这个会话的历史。\n\n不过实际上，用户问的可能是：\n1. 如何恢复之前的会话配置（渠道配置等）\n2. 如何查看之前的聊天记录\n\n让我先解释一下情况，然后提供恢复建议。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，我来帮你查看之前的会话情况！\n\n从系统状态看，你之前有两个会话：\n1. **当前会话** (`agent:main:main`) — WebChat 直接会话，正在使用中\n2. **Telegram 群组会话** (`agent:main:telegram:group:@webchat…`) — 13 小时前活跃\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_daa61cc0cd824a03a18323be","name":"sessions_history","arguments":{"sessionKey":"agent:main:telegram:group:@webchat","limit":20}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen-portal","model":"coder-model","usage":{"input":15023,"output":522,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15545,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772878604511}}
{"type":"message","id":"e056714e","parentId":"e9e22747","timestamp":"2026-03-07T10:16:49.675Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_daa61cc0cd824a03a18323be","toolName":"sessions_history","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"forbidden\",\n  \"error\": \"Session history visibility is restricted to the current session tree (tools.sessions.visibility=tree).\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"forbidden","error":"Session history visibility is restricted to the current session tree (tools.sessions.visibility=tree)."},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772878609671}}
{"type":"message","id":"238f80eb","parentId":"e056714e","timestamp":"2026-03-07T10:16:54.498Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看来我无法直接访问 Telegram 群组会话的历史记录，因为权限限制（tools.sessions.visibility=tree）。\n\n让我向用户解释情况，并提供恢复建议。用户问的是\"聊天记录对应的配置如何恢复\"，可能指的是：\n1. 恢复之前的渠道配置（Telegram）\n2. 恢复之前的会话状态\n3. 查看之前的聊天记录\n\n我需要解释当前的情况并给出建议。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了！我这边无法直接访问 Telegram 群组会话的历史（权限限制），但我可以帮你恢复配置：\n\n**恢复之前配置的方法：**\n\n1. **查看会话文件**（手动查看历史记录）：\n   ```bash\n   # 查看所有会话配置文件\n   ls -la ~/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/\n   \n   # 查看会话索引\n   cat ~/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/sessions.json\n   ```\n\n2. **恢复 Telegram 渠道配置**（如果已丢失）：\n   ```bash\n   # 检查渠道配置\n   openclaw channels list\n   \n   # 如果 Telegram 未启用，重新启用\n   openclaw channels enable telegram\n   ```\n\n3. **恢复 WebChat 渠道**（当前需要的）：\n   ```bash\n   openclaw channels enable webchat\n   ```\n\n4. **查看完整会话状态**：\n   ```bash\n   openclaw status --all\n   ```\n\n**关于聊天记录：**\n- 所有会话历史都保存在 `~/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/` 目录下的 `.jsonl` 文件中\n- 每个会话有一个独立的转录文件，可以手动查看\n\n你想恢复哪个渠道的配置？还是想查看之前的聊天记录内容？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen-portal","model":"coder-model","usage":{"input":15396,"output":437,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15833,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772878609676}}
